## 🏆 Milestone 4: The "Inventory Visualizer"

Build a warehouse inventory management system using a Linked List.
* Each item (struct) has an ID, Name, Quantity, and Price.
* Users can add items, but the Linked List must **always remain sorted** by ID upon insertion.
* Implement a Binary Search function to find an item by its ID instantly.
* Provide an option to generate a report, sorting the items by Price using Merge Sort.